        public java.lang.String getStartTime()
        Returns the moment in UTC time when the attacks can start (a day after preparation time).

        The moment is expressed in ISO-8601 standard in the following form: yyyyMMdd'T'HHmmss.SSS'Z'
        Returns:
        a String

      • getState

        public java.lang.String getState()
        Returns a String of the war state for this clan.
        Returns:
        inWar if the clan is currently in attacking time
        preparation if the clan is currently in preparation time
        warEnded if the war has already occurred
        notInWar if the clan is not involved in any war
